Name: Sergeant Whiskerbyte
Description: Hailing from the digital realm of WebtrES, Sergeant Whiskerbyte is a formidable presence with his feline-inspired box chassis and the disciplined stance of a seasoned soldier. His buttons purr with precision, and his arms and legs are always at the ready, prepared for any mission that comes his way. With a screen that gleams with the intensity of a laser, this cybernetic cat has a glare that can cut through the toughest of codes. Known for his tactical prowess and unshakable poise, Sergeant Whiskerbyte is the go-to operative when the club faces challenges that require a sharp mind and an even sharper focus.
